Package: livelink
Title: Encode Data for WASM REPL Environments
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("James Joseph", "Balamuta", , "james.balamuta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates shareable links for R code in WebAssembly (WASM) REPL environments like webR
    and for Shiny applications using Shinylive. Supports single scripts, multi-file projects, 
    exercise/solution pairs, and batch processing for both R and Python environments.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://r-pkg.thecoatlessprofessor.com/livelink/
